WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.280
We have to know

00:00:07.079 --> 00:00:11.152
that truth is what it is.

00:00:12.179 --> 00:00:14.318
We cannot conceptualize it

00:00:14.318 --> 00:00:16.735
with our human awareness.

00:00:17.097 --> 00:00:20.297
We cannot order it.

00:00:20.722 --> 00:00:23.294
We cannot manipulate it.

00:00:23.561 --> 00:00:26.867
We cannot organize it.

00:00:27.233 --> 00:00:31.360
It is what it is, has been, and will be.

00:00:32.037 --> 00:00:34.850
And what is the truth?

00:00:35.526 --> 00:00:41.342
Truth is that we are surrounded,

00:00:41.790 --> 00:00:43.655
or we are penetrated,

00:00:43.781 --> 00:00:45.953
or we are nourished,

00:00:46.095 --> 00:00:48.517
looked after and loved,

00:00:48.816 --> 00:00:52.427
by a very subtle energy

00:00:53.029 --> 00:00:59.145
which is the energy of Divine love.

00:01:00.845 --> 00:01:02.918
The second truth is

00:01:03.343 --> 00:01:06.389
that we are not this body,

00:01:06.436 --> 00:01:09.636
this mind,

00:01:10.053 --> 00:01:12.249
these conditionings,

00:01:12.375 --> 00:01:14.197
this ego,

00:01:14.260 --> 00:01:18.775
but we are the Spirit.

00:01:20.477 --> 00:01:25.425
You don't have to accept what I am saying blindly,

00:01:25.850 --> 00:01:30.702
because blind faith leads to fanaticism.

00:01:31.189 --> 00:01:35.091
But as scientists, you must keep your mind open

00:01:35.386 --> 00:01:39.222
and see for yourself what I am saying.

00:01:39.568 --> 00:01:45.932
If it is so, honestly you must accept it.

00:01:50.828 --> 00:01:54.395
We know so much through science

00:01:55.071 --> 00:01:59.150
about our civilisation,

00:01:59.933 --> 00:02:05.259
our advancement.

00:02:06.239 --> 00:02:09.953
This is the advancement of a tree

00:02:10.546 --> 00:02:13.701
which has grown outside very much.

00:02:13.890 --> 00:02:18.258
But if we do not know our roots,

00:02:19.887 --> 00:02:22.478
we'll be destroyed.

00:02:22.826 --> 00:02:27.179
So it is important to know about our roots.

00:02:27.997 --> 00:02:31.189
And this is what it is,

00:02:32.067 --> 00:02:38.530
that I would say are our roots.

00:02:40.464 --> 00:02:46.374
As you can see there are seven centres within us

00:02:50.648 --> 00:02:57.931
and these subtle centres are placed

00:02:58.579 --> 00:03:02.669
in the spinal cord and in the brain.

00:03:05.802 --> 00:03:10.722
These cater to our physical, mental,
emotional, and spiritual needs.

00:03:12.223 --> 00:03:15.733
On the physical side, they manifest

00:03:15.990 --> 00:03:19.622
the energy for the use of our plexuses

00:03:19.948 --> 00:03:26.372
which look after our physical problems.

00:03:27.707 --> 00:03:30.285
That is on the right side.

00:03:32.326 --> 00:03:37.926
This energy which is supplied by this yellow line,

00:03:38.710 --> 00:03:44.990
a subtle channel, we call it as the Pingala Nadi.

00:03:46.452 --> 00:03:52.640
This supplies energy for our physical
and mental actions.

00:03:53.168 --> 00:03:57.663
So this is the power of action within us

00:03:58.010 --> 00:04:00.150
which also caters

00:04:00.292 --> 00:04:04.313
to the right sympathetic nervous system.

00:04:05.522 --> 00:04:09.368
The another channel you see on the left hand side

00:04:09.603 --> 00:04:13.994
is the channel by which we desire.

00:04:14.555 --> 00:04:17.082
Put our energy to our desire.

00:04:17.239 --> 00:04:19.580
So this is the power of desire

00:04:19.722 --> 00:04:23.229
and looks after our emotions.

00:04:24.144 --> 00:04:27.007
This is the one which

00:04:27.243 --> 00:04:30.606
looks after our conditionings, also.

00:04:31.142 --> 00:04:35.761
At the end of these two channels they create

00:04:36.170 --> 00:04:38.488
two institutions.

00:04:39.218 --> 00:04:41.727
One on the right side crosses over,

00:04:42.795 --> 00:04:46.267
and the yellow balloon that you see is the ego.

00:04:46.393 --> 00:04:49.145
Is the balloon of ego that we have.

00:04:49.516 --> 00:04:51.891
And the left-hand side one,

00:04:52.017 --> 00:04:55.235
which conditions our mind,

00:04:55.723 --> 00:04:58.532
is the balloon of superego.

00:05:00.610 --> 00:05:03.342
As we start growing in age,

00:05:03.342 --> 00:05:05.653
by the time we are 12 years of age,

00:05:06.093 --> 00:05:08.093
these two completely meet

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:18.000
and the soft bone in our head becomes
completely calcified.

00:05:21.979 --> 00:05:24.624
Now there is a third energy within us

00:05:26.717 --> 00:05:28.923
which is in the centre.

00:05:30.213 --> 00:05:35.762
And this central energy is the one
which has made us human beings,

00:05:36.910 --> 00:05:42.792
and these centres are the milestones
of our evolution.

00:05:44.444 --> 00:05:51.527
So now the last jumping is left out.

00:05:52.958 --> 00:05:55.880
It has reached up to the limbic area.

00:05:58.743 --> 00:06:03.733
Now, only thing, it has to break through

00:06:04.221 --> 00:06:12.136
the soft bone on the head

00:06:15.110 --> 00:06:17.812
and break through that.